    <item>
      <title>纽约市准备迎接一场大雨和大风的强大风暴</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-17/nyc-braces-for-a-powerful-storm-packing-heavy-rain-and-winds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一场席卷美国东海岸的强大风暴即将在周一早上的高峰时段袭击纽约市，带来大雨、大面积洪水、强风足以延误航空旅行并导致停电的威胁。但 12 月中旬的天气预报并不包括降雪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-17/nyc-braces-for-a-powerful-storm-packing-heavy-rain-and-winds</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 13:55:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯天然气工业股份公司表示，输往中国的天然气流量创下单日新纪录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-17/russia-s-gazprom-says-gas-delivery-to-china-set-new-daily-record</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯天然气工业股份公司(Gazprom PJSC)周日表示，前一天创下了向中国供应天然气的单日新纪录，突显了这个巨大邻国在乌克兰战争中几乎失去欧洲市场后的重要性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-17/russia-s-gazprom-says-gas-delivery-to-china-set-new-daily-record</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 11:15:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
